  <fr:mainmatter>
 <fr:p>By induction on <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>, with the base cases following from <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-003V.xml" title="Dependent sum of contractible types" addr="//erct/erct-003V" type="local">Corollary <fr:contextual-number addr="//erct/erct-003V" /></fr:link> and <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001M.xml" title="Dependent sum of propositions" addr="//erct/erct-001M" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number addr="//erct/erct-001M" /></fr:link>. In the inductive step, we need to show that for all <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[u,v\colon \mathchoice {\textstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
