}}Bx]]></fr:tex> the identification type <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[u=v]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001G.xml" title="n-truncated type" addr="//erct/erct-001G" type="local"><html:span style="white-space: nowrap" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n+1]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span></fr:link> assuming the same of all the identification types of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[Bx]]></fr:tex> for <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x:A]]></fr:tex>. By <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-0035.xml" title="Covariant sum of a left-cloven family of path objects" addr="//erct/erct-0035" type="local">Definition <fr:contextual-number addr="//erct/erct-0035" /></fr:link>, <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[u=v]]></fr:tex> is a <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-0025.xml" title="Retract" addr="//erct/erct-0025" type="local">retract</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \sum _{
