            <fr:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {B}\colon  
 \mathopen {}\left \lvert \mathcal {A}\right \rvert \mathclose {}
\to  \mathsf {PathObj}]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-0031.xml" title="Left cleaving of a family of path objects" addr="//erct/erct-0031" type="local">left-cloven family of path objects</fr:link> over a <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-0010.xml" title="Path object" addr="//erct/erct-0010" type="local">path object</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {A}]]></fr:tex>. We define the <fr:em><fr:strong>covariant sum</fr:strong></fr:em> of the family <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {B}]]></fr:tex>, written <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \oint _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathcal {A}\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \oint _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathcal {A}\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \oint _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathcal {A}\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \oint _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathcal {A}\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\mathcal {B} x}]]></fr:tex>, to be the <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-0018.xml" title="The total path object of a displayed path object" addr="//erct/erct-0018" type="local">total path object</fr:link> of the <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-0012.xml" title="Displayed path object" addr="//erct/erct-0012" type="local">displayed path object</fr:link> associated to <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {B}]]></fr:tex> by <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-0033.xml" title="Display of left-cloven families of path objects" addr="//erct/erct-0033" type="local">Definition <fr:contextual-number addr="//erct/erct-0033" /></fr:link>. In particular, we have defined <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x,u\right \rparen \mathclose {}
\approx _{\mathchoice {\textstyle \oint _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathcal {A}\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \oint _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathcal {A}\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \oint _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathcal {A}\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \oint _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:\mathcal {A}\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\mathcal {B} x}}
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen y,v\right \rparen \mathclose {}
]]></fr:tex> to be <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen p : x\approx _{\mathcal {A}} y\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen p : x\approx _{\mathcal {A}} y\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen p : x\approx _{\mathcal {A}} y\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \sum _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen p : x\approx _{\mathcal {A}} y\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}} p_*u \approx _{\mathcal {B} y} v]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
